  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1940 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The framed leaflet features a graphic illustration showing Pinocchio and an elderly man on a primitive raft in stormy water. They are both holding a paddle in their right hands. A seagull is depicted in the top right corner, where the English original film title ‘Pinocchio’ is spelt in Serbo-Croatian: ‘Pinokio’</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The number ‘10’ noted in handwriting on the top right corner is 
probably an outdated registration number. The film was directed by Norman Ferguson et al. and was released in 1940.</ab>
